Kingdom''' - [[Aberdeen Airport|Aberdeen]], [[Blackpool Airport|Blackpool]], [[Bristol Airport|Bristol]], [[Durham Tees Valley Airport|Durham Tees Valley]], [[East Midlands Airport|East Midlands]], [[Edinburgh International Airport|Edinburgh]], [[Glasgow Airport|Glasgow]], [[London Stansted Airport|London-Stansted]], [[Newcastle International Airport|Newcastle upon Tyne]], [[Newquay Cornwall Airport|Newquay]]\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|http://www.monarch.co.uk/}}{{dead link|date=February 2018}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2010}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Monarch Airlines Destinations}}\n[[Category:Lists of airline destinations]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n\n{{refimprove|date=February 2018}}\n[[File:Airbus A321-231, Monarch Airlines JP7651538.jpg|thumb|Monarch Airlines [[Airbus A321|Airbus A321-200]]]]\n[[Monarch Airlines]] served the following destinations at the time when it ceased operations in October 2017.<ref>[http://www.monarch.co.uk/destinations monarch.co.uk - Where We Fly To] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100204080432/http://www.monarch.co.uk/destinations |date=4 February 2010 }} 9 May 2015</ref>\n\n==Europe==\n;Austria\n*[[Innsbruck]] \u2013 [[Innsbruck Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n*[[Salzburg]] \u2013 [[Salzburg Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n\n;Croatia\n*[[Dubrovnik]] \u2013 [[Dubrovnik Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n*[[Split, Croatia|Split]] - [[Split Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n*[[Zagreb]] \u2013 [[Zagreb Airport]]\n\n;Cyprus\n*[[Larnaca]] \u2013 [[Larnaca Airport]]\n*[[Paphos]] \u2013 [[Paphos Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n\n;Finland\n*[[Kittil\u00e4]] \u2013 [[Kittil\u00e4 Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n\n;France\n*[[Lyon]] \u2013 [[Lyon\u2013Saint-Exup\u00e9ry Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n*[[Grenoble]] \u2013 [[Grenoble-Is\u00e8re Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n*[[Nice]] \u2013 [[C\u00f4te d'Azur Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n\n;Greece\n*[[Heraklion]] \u2013 [[Heraklion Airport]] ''Seasonal''\n*[[Preveza]]